<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🏘️ Builder Basics — Complete Your Village (Extension · Beginner)</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Bring It All Together · <strong>Course:</strong> Builder Basics · <strong>Level:</strong> Beginner · <strong>Type:</strong> Extension Activity · <strong>Time:</strong> about 30 minutes</p>
<blockquote>
<p>🧩 A bonus challenge, not a weekly lesson. Try it after the Week 8 village.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<h2>1 · The Challenge 🎯</h2>
<p>Finish your village. It must have <strong>all four</strong> of these:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>🏠 House with a roof
🪣 Well
💧 Small pond
🌸 Small flower bed</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>One rule: build with _____. Circle one:</strong> code · your hands</p>
<p><strong>Tick each one when it is done in your world:</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>☐ 🏠 House with a roof
☐ 🪣 Well
☐ 💧 Small pond
☐ 🌸 Small flower bed</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<h2>2 · Match It 🔗</h2>
<p><strong>A pond is made of a dip in the ground filled with… Circle one:</strong> water · lava · flowers</p>
<p><strong>A flower bed is a row of… Circle one:</strong> flowers · doors · stairs</p>
<p><strong>A house needs a roof so it has a… Circle one:</strong> top · hole · door</p>
<hr />
<h2>3 · Use a Loop 🔁</h2>
<p>A loop repeats the same step again and again.</p>
<p><strong>Which one is best made with a loop? Circle one:</strong> one door · a row of flowers · one block</p>
<p><strong>Between the house and the pond, the agent must first… Circle one:</strong> walk to a new spot · stop · turn off</p>
<hr />
<h2>4 · Build It, Then Show It 📸🎥</h2>
<p>Go to your world. Build all four with code: the <strong>house with a roof</strong>, the <strong>well</strong>, the <strong>small pond</strong>, and the <strong>small flower bed</strong>.</p>
<p>Then take a video on your phone (or a parent's phone). In your video:</p>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>Point to each of the four things and say its name: <strong>house, well, pond, flower bed</strong>.</li>
<li>Show the flower bed and say: "I used a <strong>loop</strong> to place the row of flowers."</li>
<li>Say which one you like best.</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<p>Send a photo <strong>and</strong> the video to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
<hr />
<h3>Submit ✅</h3>
<p>Send this worksheet + your video to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
<div class="footer">영어코딩 · <b>english-coding.co.uk</b></div>
</div></body></html>
